Repositories - Image Sensors

List of image sensors with mainline kernel support (this is also present in file Camera and Image Sensor):
(Note that the directory is named "i2c" but this includes MIPI CSI-2 image sensors)
https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/next/linux-next.git/tree/drivers/media/i2c
https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/next/linux-next.git/tree/drivers/media/i2c?h=next-20250505

AR1335 (Used by Debix Camera 1300A) Driver for NXP i.MX Chips
https://github.com/nxp-imx/isp-vvcam/tree/lf-6.12.y_1.0.0/vvcam/v4l2/sensor/ar1335

Sony IMX 708 Image Sensor used in the Raspberry Pi RPi V3 Camera
 in RPi Tree
  Overlays
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/imx708-overlay.dts
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/imx708.dtsi
  YAML
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/media/i2c/sony%2Cimx708.yaml
  Driver in C
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/drivers/media/i2c/imx708.c
 in Torvalds's Tree (mainline)
  Overlays (in git.uk.IdeasOnBoard.com tree not Torvalds's Tree)
   https://git.uk.ideasonboard.com/camera/dt-overlays/commit/de028032947cad5905cc55865196bef2d24b398f

RidgeRun Driver for Sony IMX708 Image Sensor in RPi V3 Camera Written for NVIDIA
 https://github.com/RidgeRun/NVIDIA-Jetson-IMX708-RPIV3
 Detailled article on the above:
 https://developer.ridgerun.com/wiki/index.php/Raspberry_Pi_Camera_Module_3_IMX708_Linux_driver_for_Jetson

Sony IMX 219 Image Sensor used in the Raspberry Pi RPi V2 Camera
 in RPi Tree
  Overlays
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/imx219-overlay.dts
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/arch/arm/boot/dts/overlays/imx219.dtsi
  YAML
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/media/i2c/imx219.yaml
  Driver in C
   https://github.com/raspberrypi/linux/blob/rpi-6.12.y/drivers/media/i2c/imx219.c
 in Torvalds's Tree (mainline)
  Overlays (in IdeasOnBoard tree not Torvalds's Tree)
   https://gitlab.com/ideasonboard/nxp/linux/-/commit/2e3ab4d9815eaca81c236924d3393c7ced345619
  YAML
   https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/tree/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/media/i2c/sony,imx219.yaml
  Driver in C in Torvalds's Tree (mainline)
   https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/tree/drivers/media/i2c/imx219.c

DTOs (Device Tree Overlays) for the Debix 200a camera, Debix 500a camera and IMX335 image sensor for the i.MX 8 M Plus:
Note that these were written for the Debix Model A SBC so may need to be adjusted for the Debix Model A SoM and Debix Model A SoM I/O board.
https://git.uk.ideasonboard.com/camera/dt-overlays/src/branch/main/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale

https://gitlab.com/ideasonboard/nxp/linux/-/commit/2e3ab4d9815eaca81c236924d3393c7ced345619

